The '''''Rimrunner''''', a modified [[CorelliSpace]] [[Gymsnor-4 light freighter]], was the personal ship of of the smuggler [[Salla Zend]]. The most notable modification was a pair of aft-firing [[Concussion missile/Legends|concussion missile]] launchers, which provided a nasty surprise for any pursuing ship. The ''Rimrunner'' played an important role in the [[Battle of Nar Shaddaa (4 BBY)|Battle of Nar Shaddaa]], but was later destroyed during a botched [[Kessel Run/Legends|Kessel Run]]. While racing against [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo's]] [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']], Salla skirted too close to one of [[Maw Cluster/Legends|the Maw's]] [[Black hole/Legends|black holes]] while attempting a [[Precision hyperspace jump|micro-jump]]. Han came to Salla's rescue and both barely escaped with their lives, the ''Rimrunner'' however couldn't be saved.

